[thinking] 
[thinking] I’m considering using a native image module, but that feels risky and maybe not worth it. An alternative could be to create a separate package that's not open and use `module-info` within `src/test/java`. I think the build process would likely infer the necessary connections. It makes sense to look into other modular tests within the repository to see how they manage this. Let's gather more information!
[thinking] 
