er$ModuleSystemFound` paths:\n  - `injectionBase(...)`\n  - carrier field lookup and assignment\n  - generated module adjustment probe initialization\n\nI did not run the Gradle test locally, per workflow instruction.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0a6beee47f3b5c1b016a2c122f48848197bd550d7579a73ece\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 2809, "output": 1216, "cacheRead": 49664, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 53689, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1781273112395, "responseId": "resp_0a6beee47f3b5c1b016a2c12192918819795ead7918737011b"}}
